Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really looking forward to the fireflies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They should hurry up and come sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:21.79,Signs,,0,0,0,,Owada Michitake (47)\NChief Priest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, Owada speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:24.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Nakamine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.91,0:00:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nakamine-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Firefly Song...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:35.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because we're driving carefully, we might arrive later than planned...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we've passed the Akazawa Bridge,\Nand will be there in about 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:42.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.51,0:00:45.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakamine-kun, make sure you guys drive carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:47.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.31,0:00:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:51.19,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\be5\fad(250,210)}Nakamine Tokurou (28)\NVillage Head's Son
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:54.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HA22628&\blur2\be5\}Flowers dance to the piano's rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HA22628&\blur2\be5\}Two people face-to-face is a mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:00:59.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HA22628&\blur2\be5\}The young are clashing about\Namidst the  village revitalization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HA22628&\blur2\be5}The flicker of the fireflies will shine the truth to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\bord0.1\blur1\xshad1.3\1c&H6AE8FA&\4c&H294A50&\}Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\bord0.1\blur1\xshad1.3\1c&H6AE8FA&\4c&H294A50&\}The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:07.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)\bord0.1\blur1\xshad1.3\1c&H6AE8FA&\4c&H294A50&\}His name is: Detective {\t(1450,1451,\1c&H4331B1&)}Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he'll be here in 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:03.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to see the fireflies now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fireflies serve as the trump card of this village's sightseeing spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of the villagers are excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the shrine that gathered tourist interest before, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People were pretty crazy about a shrine that's inside a cave...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they aren't anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Priest Owada-san here came\Nup with the idea of breeding fireflies...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was difficult to raise funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:32.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you did manage that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's all thanks to the village head's son, Nakamine-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the matter regarding Aoi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}He said that in exchange for his fundraising\Nservice, he wants to marry my daughter Aoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And how did Aoi reply?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She gave him the cold shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:55.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nakamine-kun abuses the fact\Nthat he's the village head's son...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:57.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}He beats people up and fools around with women.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:50.87,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\be5\fad(250,250)}Owada Aoi (22)\NMichitake's Daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:57.71,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\be5\fad(250,0)}Kashiwa Tatsuma (26)\N{\fs13}Eldest Son of an Old Family in the Village
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since he's the youth group's leader,\Nhe still helps us at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, turn off the streetlights!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:28.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Tarumi-kun, thanks for the good work.\h
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an3}It's nothing.\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:30.79,Signs,,0,0,0,,Tarumi Shuuichirou (26)\NNakamine's Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Nakamine-kun, I thank you too...\h\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tarumi, you can open them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:56.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike the city, it's dark here so we can see clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:57.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll catch ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you, firefly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:24.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A firefly's mouth is undeveloped, so it can only ingest water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once the nutrient it stored during its larval form is used up, it dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.72,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\be5\fad(0,0)}Narutaki Souichi (59)\NPolice Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Narutaki-san, so you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:46.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Priest Owada-san, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How pretty these are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but to think how nice\Nit'd be if I could show Mayu these.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.09,0:06:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How unfortunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A landslide struck his house last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:18.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He lost his family because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mentioned that in the letter you sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About a man who lost his cute granddaughter because of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that was Narutaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a local police detective, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:33.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really gave me the creeps; the road was narrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Nakamine-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:38.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where could he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:42.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:46.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this Nakamine-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:53.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, who's over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did Nakamine-kun say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All he said was "I'm at Eboshi Rock, help me!" in a painful voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:03.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's this Eboshi Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:05.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a rock upstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's take the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The keys... the keys are missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps Nakamine-san took them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakamine-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakamine-san, you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scent of almond...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it cyanide poisoning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:15.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A drink bottle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it poisoned?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A firefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While we wait for the local backup to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:30.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's summarize the chain of events in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After carrying the fireflies here, Nakamine-san\Nwent missing for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Tarumi-san called him, he merely said\Nthat he was at Eboshi Rock and in agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sounded like someone else was present.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:51.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you guys rushed there, you saw Nakamine-san\Nin his car, his breathing already ceased.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Nakamine-san couldn't have driven alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His right leg seemed to be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, after he released the fireflies,\Nsomeone else drove him to Eboshi Rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he was given the poisoned drink and murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did that firefly get in while they were boarding the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:23.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We wanted to help with the investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Detective Boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Children are not allowed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you guys to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:34.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think Narutaki-san was reminded of his granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was surprised when I saw you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Mayu was my look-alike who died in the landslide?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mountain collapses easily nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too many trees have been cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever the rain gets heavy, my heart jumps in fright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:06.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:07.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aoi, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:12.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did you go off to after the fireflies were released?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:18.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to believe it, but did you meet with Nakamine-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:24.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When it comes to that man, I can't stop worrying about what he'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kashiwa-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to Kashiwa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to Tarumi-kun, he was being picked on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Tatsuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As the village's oldest noble family, your donation was too stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your late father would definitely frown upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't talk so loud, people will hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my normal voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:59.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the Kashiwa family could help out more, it'd\Nbe easier for me to gather funds from people!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Tarumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said, the village revitalization all depends on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, my, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the village head's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:11.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss, it's been quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:16.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be so formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:22.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsuma, hurry up and invite him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was scolded severely by his mother later on:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:29.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Why didn't you help with the village revitalization?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His mother didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That her late husband almost bankrupted the family with his debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:38.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me remind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though you and Kashiwa-kun are childhood\Nfriends, I disallow you marrying each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In a family headed toward turmoil, and with a\Nmother like that, I can only foresee you suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:00.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful, it's very slippery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:04.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A shrine inside a cave, how incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:07.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could there be fireflies around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}♪ Come, come, come, fireflies... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}♪The water there is bitter...♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I could hear the firefly song back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, Owada speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Nakamine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:24.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nakamine-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Boys, let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be scolded by the detective again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:34.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not here, so we should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's right inside the shrine office!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their local backup has arrived, and they're\Nabout to start a thorough investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did they find out something new?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, about the drink bottle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:50.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The drink was Nakamine-san's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the bottle left at the scene had its contents washed clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was washed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:13:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aoi, you're there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shrine office uses that to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aoi, the police wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be frank...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:33.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to our interview taken since last night,\Nwe found out something unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The priest forgot to turn off the mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.49,0:13:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For an entire 30 minutes after the fireflies' release,\Nno one witnessed Aoi-san's presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:48.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, it was in the time span before\Nthe victim's body was discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Narutaki-san, in the darkness like that, it wouldn't\Nbe a surprise if no one had seen my daughter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, after some investigation, everyone\Nelse confirmed each other's presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because people often huddle together during firefly-watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Within a confined space, I may add.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite this, no one else saw Owada Aoi-san and another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:14.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Nakamine-san took a fancy in Aoi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would without a doubt follow her to Eboshi Rock if invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if she gave him the poisoned drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in that case, that could also apply to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:33.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then again, if you were the inviter, I don't\Nthink that Nakamine-san would take the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, it looks like I'm safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it, it's too early to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have something you're hiding too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakamine-san was angry with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that you embezzled funds from gathering fireflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:56.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I explained everything and Nakamine-san understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta, what's with that flashlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've had that since last night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot to return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:08.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was in that truck that brought the fireflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me take a look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:15.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall, at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:18.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakamine-kun, I thank you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tarumi, you can open them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:24.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aoi-san, do you have anything to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do have something to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:42.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agasa-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do not worry, Owada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your daughter is not the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a layperson, please refrain from interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll make it quick, but only after...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:57.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've exposed the crime that Tarumi-san committed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:16:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "my crime"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who killed Nakamine-san with poisoned drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Nakamine-san died, I was right beside you, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The phone call, in which you claimed Nakamine-san\Nwas dying, was merely your acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakamine-san was already dead before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I released the fireflies, I was with my friends the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did I go near Eboshi Rock if you're accusing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was before you released the fireflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night, we received a call from Nakamine-san\Nas he was transporting the fireflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We could hear the Firefly Song's melody from the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was coming from the grocery store halfway\Nthrough the path to Eboshi Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:58.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, Nakamine-san was headed toward Eboshi\NRock with Tarumi-san who was driving the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,4,,Then he dropped Nakamine-san off at Eboshi\NRock, and returned to the riverbank alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:05.17,Signs,,0,0,0,,Sasa Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:05.17,Signs,,0,0,0,,Grocery Store
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:05.17,Signs,,0,0,0,,Eboshi Rock
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:06.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the fireflies were about to be released,\Nwe heard Nakamine-kun's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a simple trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, isn't that a flashlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, turn off the streetlights!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tarumi, you can open them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.39,0:17:37.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a voice recorder shaped like a flashlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You used this and pretended to have a\Nconversation with Nakamine-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:46.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, that's why he didn't respond to me when I talked to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:52.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tarumi-san, just as you were about\Nto take the truck to Eboshi Rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:56.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You panicked a little when you looked inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:18:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because this thing that was supposed to be in there was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact, one of the kids accidentally kept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably lured Nakamine-san by saying this:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aoi-san wanted to meet you, but she didn't\Nwant her father to know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she wanted you to create an alibi\Nand meet her secretly at Eboshi Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakamine-san easily took the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had you take him to Eboshi Rock, and recorded\Nhis voice himself as alibi fabrication...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he got into his own car that was parked\Nbeforehand, waiting for Aoi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just then, you handed him the poisoned drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, as he was waiting for Aoi-san, he drank that and died...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:46.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:50.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I went to Eboshi Rock before releasing the fireflies...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.22,0:18:52.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did a firefly fly out of the car!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You released one into the car, just so you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was pretty bold of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You arrived at the victim's car a few steps sooner than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when you made the switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You switched the poisoned bottle for one with a firefly in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason the bottle was washed was\Nso that you could insert a firefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:26.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to the station to explain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:43.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Landslide!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:16.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:18.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Ai-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tarumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop this nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:28.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nowhere for you to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:31.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A firefly, firefly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares about a firefly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fact that the firefly came here means\Nthat there's a path to the outside, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good, it's over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:52.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you move a bit, this brat loses her life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:20:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now there are two fireflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a reflection from a puddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet Haibara notices.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:41.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Mayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayu!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.31,0:21:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not Mayu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.79,0:21:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.73,0:21:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Truly, thank goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:21:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.58,0:23:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The motive for Tarumi's wasn't just about\Nthe embezzling of the firefly fund...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he also stole money from Nakamine's father's\Ncompany, and feared that would be exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.42,0:23:38.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was afraid about what would happen back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.84,0:23:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was a happy ending, happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:51.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like a happy ending over there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.69,0:23:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:01.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Robber!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.37,0:24:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.70,0:24:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I recall, his right cheek was burnt.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.21,0:24:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there such a man during that bus jacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.29,0:24:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he was wearing a knitted cap and a mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.55,0:24:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...
